<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Invitation expirée</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body { min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #063a55, #0b4fa3); font-family:'Segoe UI', sans-serif; padding:20px; }
        .card-e { background:#fff; border-radius:16px; padding:40px; max-width:460px; width:100%; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
        .icon-e { width:80px; height:80px; margin:0 auto 18px; border-radius:50%; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); color:#fff; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:2.5rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card-e">
        <div class="icon-e"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i></div>
        <h1 style="font-weight:800; color:#0b1f3a;">Invitation invalide ou expirée</h1>
        <p style="color:#475569;">
            Ce lien d'invitation n'est plus valide (expiré 14 jours, ou déjà utilisé).<br><br>
            Demande au staff MABB de t'envoyer une nouvelle invitation.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
